Installation for Windows
=======================

X:\theTop> bin\theTop-init


Installation for *nix
=====================

$ bin/theTop-init


Start Working for Windows
=========================

X:\theTop> bin\theTop-activate


Start Working for *nix
======================

$ . bin/theTop-activate


Move Working Directory
======================

When the working directory is moved, remove THETOP_HOME/python and THETOP_HOME/buildout.cfg
and then init-python again
